---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>Client Testimonials | LEM Building Surveying</title>
    <meta name="description" content="What our clients say about LEM Building Surveying Ltd." />
  </Fragment>

  <main>
    <section class="testimonial-section">
      <h1>Client Testimonials</h1>
      <p>
        We pride ourselves on providing straightforward, independent advice that helps you move forward with confidence.
        Below is a snapshot of the feedback we regularly receive from homeowners, buyers and property professionals across
        Cheshire and North Wales.
      </p>

      <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-list">
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-rating" aria-label="Five star review">
            <span aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
          </p>
          <blockquote>
            <p>
              “We used Liam to carry out a Level 2 Survey on a property we are purchasing. We found him very responsive,
              professional and knowledgeable. Liam highlighted issues without frightening us, offering advice on how to move
              forward. Would highly recommend him.”
            </p>
            <footer>— Lindsey M.</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-rating" aria-label="Five star review">
            <span aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
          </p>
          <blockquote>
            <p>
              “LEM provided an excellent service from start to finish. His report was clear and explained everything simply and
              with enough detail for me to make informed choices. I would recommend LEM to anyone needing Building Surveying
              services.”
            </p>
            <footer>— Chris S.</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-rating" aria-label="Five star review">
            <span aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
          </p>
          <blockquote>
            <p>
              “Liam was fantastic—professional, efficient, and really knowledgeable. He explained everything clearly, which
              made the whole process much easier. I’d definitely recommend LEM Building Surveying to anyone needing EPCs,
              floorplans, or a property survey. A smooth and stress-free experience from start to finish!”
            </p>
            <footer>— Helen H.</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
      </div>

      <p>
        You can explore our latest verified reviews below. The live feed updates automatically, so you always see recent
        feedback from people who have instructed LEM Building Surveying Ltd.
      </p>
      <div class="ti-widget ti-goog"></div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
